<p>A friend's loss can leave us feeling helpless. These messages are designed to convey empathy and support to those grieving a cherished friendship.  Let these words remind them of your unwavering friendship and care.</p>
<li>I'm so incredibly sorry for your loss, my dear friend.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending all my love during this hard time.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you. Please know I’m here for you always.</li>
<li>I can only imagine the pain you’re going through.</li>
<li>May your memories of [friend's name] bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace as you grieve.</li>
<li>Your friendship meant so much to me. I’ll cherish the memories.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, now and always. Let's talk when you're ready.</li>
<li>I'm deeply saddened by your loss; you're in my thoughts.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincere condolences.</li>
